{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0b233c2ffc","title":"在有利条件下攻击水头之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"29111cb936","index":0,"year":1936,"month":2,"day":26,"articleId":"0b233c2ffc"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cbd9bcdd61","type":"paragraph","text":"在有利条件下攻击水头之敌”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"0b233c2ffc"},{"id":"38a3d867fb","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年2月26日）徐、程：甲、明日你们向水头P前进，须先侦察，看地形有利，敌无堡绝险地或工事之依靠，然后攻击之，否则不应开始攻击。又须看时间许可，能解决战斗，然后攻击之，否则不应攻击，即在水头附近宿营。乙、一军团本日十四时才赶到关上，战未几即天黑，时政渍退入工事与村房内，尚未解决战斗。已令他们明目相机消灭该敌或撤退至关上、水头间地区","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"0b233c2ffc"},{"id":"0881e9d113","type":"paragraph","text":"彭毛","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"0b233c2ffc"},{"id":"0f8bb663a5","type":"paragraph","text":"二十六日二十三时H这是毛泽东和红军第一方面军司令员彭德怀给第一方面军第十五军团军团长徐毒东、政治委员程子华的电报。[2]水头，镇名，位于今山西省交口县西北。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"0b233c2ffc"}],"page":{"id":"fc34d083ad","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"0b233c2ffc","start":265,"end":265}}}},"__N_SSG":true}